text: Skunk weed may refer to: * Skunk (cannabis), a selection of selectively bred cannabis strains, scent comes from naturally occurring acids that are reminiscent of barnyard animals. Also acts as natural insecticide. ==Other plants== * Navarretia squarrosa, California stinkweed * Polemonium viscosum, Sky pilot * Symplocarpus foetidus, Eastern skunk cabbage * Croton texensis, Skunk weed
title: Skunk weed
